            <title>[CASSANDRA-14425] cassandra-stress doesn&apos;t report correctly when profile file is not found</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14425</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
